# Views

Read [app/views/AGENTS.md](../../app/views/AGENTS.md) and [docs/FRONTEND.md](../../docs/FRONTEND.md).

- ERB + Rails helpers + Tailwind CSS 4 first.
- No business logic in templates; no inline JS when Stimulus fits.
- Shared partials under `app/views/**/components/` when reuse is real.
- User-facing copy ready for I18n; technical text in English.
- No view specs unless policy explicitly changes.

